{"tid":1506222,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"呢張圖真睇到嬲同傷心！","createTime":"2019-08-25T17:44:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T23:38:14.000Z","uid":56682,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"70935d4d7a8a3056327bf788c161090ad2fc979b","tid":1506222,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:44:28.000Z","msg":"一張圖解釋哂點解我地會輸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1504812\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1504812</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2B6VfZE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2B6VfZE.jpg&h=f330e7f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當有手足俾狗咬住，你哋一班偽前線居然諗走人？<br />\n對唔對得住幾位烈士？<br />\n我哋仲有幾多勇武兄弟可以俾人拉？<br />\n咁多兄弟拘留時俾狗打到入院，你哋對唔對得住？<br />\n<br />\n首先，我唔敢話偽前線無用，而且作用仲好大，例如可以人多在前線為勇武壯膽等等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由呢幅圖已經可以清楚睇到兩個重點<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1.前線人員位置太少空隙</span></span><br />\n圖中後面班人根本走唔到，個個見到走唔到塞死就緊係驚喇。仲提咩救人？<br />\n後面班人唔好淨係識坐吓企吓，一係就鬆少少，一係就儘量企旁邊幫手運吓物質，中間儘量唔好企，留條通道<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2.明明有人數優勢，卻偏偏唔用</span></span><br />\n明明得一隻狗，我理得你後面係咪有大量狗沖嚟，但示威者一定多人過佢<br />\n點解唔可以好似721主動進攻？（前題必定要有盾陣for擋像膠子彈）/小型水馬擋水炮車<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以揾啲人用遠攻戰略，拖延狗隻衝擊時間，再同時揾啲勇武去解救咗兄弟先？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新口號：不分化，不篤灰，不割席，更不放棄兄弟</span></span>"},{"pid":"cc90dd841a7a94b194dfec15dd708d6d3584f437","tid":1506222,"uid":202889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:45:40.000Z","msg":"借po <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小心個袋俾狗咬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1506145/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1506145/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"d728b04a9792ad3ead9c7d8ef64c7a83be1e90e5","tid":1506222,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:46:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc09522b7d9585901392da50b0d8ffff0b41ef36","tid":1506222,"uid":56682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:47:08.000Z","msg":"見到幅相真係好嬲"},{"pid":"4c5a7bcc59eba6af5d5cacf983896cdb79ee5c97","tid":1506222,"uid":73143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:47:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚嬲 班偽前線"},{"pid":"a48a6636b3b9989769483d649622af4e9113d3bf","tid":1506222,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:50:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ac72298af39a03c28110cadf03c7ec15e490238","tid":1506222,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2865dde8c41b60eaed2c0805e9a28bf78973a3b1","tid":1506222,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:08:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e444e424826754449203e5da5d7b4886cec3bd","tid":1506222,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T22:45:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae3559798bf9cd01fcc422d6ffeb8d8fef1eb8c0","tid":1506222,"uid":4875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T22:47:00.000Z","msg":"睇翻原片啦，隻狗後面成百幾防暴，你回頭救死傷仲多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"921f0d916120a0e7411bc95606cf73fb40039e06","tid":1506222,"uid":1